# The Complete Rant: 17 Problems We Encountered and How We Solved Them

This document serves as an exhaustive chronicle of every single bug, crash, bottleneck, architectural failure, and deployment trap we fought during the development and deployment of **RedisRAG** (FastAPI + React + Redis Vector DB + Render + Vercel).

---

